The paper deals with geometric algorithms and Voronoi diagrams, which are typical topics in computational geometry (cs.CG). The use of approximation algorithms and local search also suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of algorithms and complexity (cs.DS), discrete mathematics (cs.DM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and game theory (cs.GT).
